Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:43.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Refrain　消した記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:49.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Rely　物語の常が今見せる言葉で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Don't end this, won't change it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}どうしたって　変えられない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:57.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}目的を忘れないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:05.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}誰が決めたんだ　そんな生き方らしくないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:11.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}やりたいこと貫く力　それこそが強さだって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:15.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}分かっているから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I believe in what I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}No reason to go back again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:24.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}歩んできた日々を　懐かしむ意味を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Easy losing memories
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I'm struggling now to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:33.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}諦めることはない　最後まで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Get down, let's get down
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:42.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}心の光を　覚えてるうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:46.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Trust yourself. Don't be naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:51.25,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Save yourself. Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:43.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Refrain 抹去的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:49.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Rely 故事總在隻言片語間展開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Don't end this, won't change it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}無論怎麼做都無法改變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:57.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}但不要忘記你的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:05.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}別人定義出的你 不是真實的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:11.29,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}堅持自我的力量 才是真的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:15.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}這就是我的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I believe in what I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}No reason to go back again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:24.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}我會回憶走過的路 找出價值所在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Easy losing memories
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I'm struggling now to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:33.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}我會堅持到最後 不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Get down, let's get down
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:42.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}趁你心裡還亮著一團光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:46.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Trust yourself. Don't be naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:51.25,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Save yourself. Don't forget.
